data.description: Welcome home to this charming cape featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, and 2 half baths, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to discover a move-in-ready haven with a freshly painted interior that exudes a sense of warmth and welcome. The entire home boasts newer flooring, providing a contemporary and cohesive look throughout. Almost all windows have been replaced, allowing natural light to flood each room and enhancing the overall aesthetic. The kitchen is a focal point of this residence, with refaced cabinets presenting a modern feel. Imagine preparing meals in this updated space equipped with appliances that are just over 2 years old. All kitchen appliances stay, ensuring a seamless transition for the new homeowner. The bathroom has been tastefully updated, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. The laundry room, located in the basement, has been recently painted. Step outside to a meticulously cared-for exterior, featuring newer concrete work, including new steps, patio, RV pad, and dedicated parking for your convenience. The newer shed, provides additional storage space, while fresh landscaping enhances the curb appeal. This home not only offers a dry basement but also a clean and well-maintained living space. It's evident the seller has ensured this property is ready for its new occupants. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home—schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and quality this property has to offer.
